<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20170930/7368030af77a48d3a35b059903f248d1.jpeg" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">五行的生克关系</span></img></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20170930/34bf91426590423792aadc884026c49c.jpeg" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">五行的生克关系</span></img></p>
